&gt;She simply gives you a sympathetic look and squeezes you even tighter.
&gt;&quot;POOR ANON... WHAT WAS IT ABOUT?&quot;
&gt;...you&#039;d really rather not say, but she deserves to know.  Heck, think about how open she&#039;s been with you.
