&gt;When you arrive, you immediately set Sesh&#039;s delivery next to her.  You think you can make out a faint smile from behind her screens.
&gt;&quot;...thank you, Anon.&quot;
&gt;Suddenly, the three heads of VHL appear on all of Sesh&#039;s displays.
